499
00:49:56,428 --> 00:49:58,138
- Evet, bayım.
- Tamam.

500
00:49:58,555 --> 00:49:59,890
Devam et.

501
00:50:04,728 --> 00:50:05,645
Şunu geri al...

502
00:50:05,896 --> 00:50:08,690
